1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Did you know your brain can strengthen connections just by repeating actions?

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:08,000
This process is called Long-Term Potentiation, or LTP.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:13,200
When you repeatedly activate a synapse, it becomes more sensitive, enhancing the signal.

4
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:17,200
Research shows LTP can last for hours, sometimes even longer.

5
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:22,000
Think about it: every time you practice, you're literally rewiring your brain.

6
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:24,800
Want to learn more about your brain?

7
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:27,200
Hit follow for more neuroscience insights!
